Title: Establishes a task force to conduct a study on the ability to utilize telehealth within the workers' compensation system
Summary: Establishes a task force to conduct a study on the ability to utilize telehealth within the workers' compensation system.
ActClause: AN ACT to establish a task force to conduct a comprehensive study on the ability to utilize telehealth within the workers' compensation system; and providing for the repeal of such provisions upon the expiration thereof
